Use the following system properties to configure the tests...

# Base path to test resources
# Defaults to... /opt/bcc/tests/datafiles
resource.path

# Path to location that screen shots should be saved in
# Defaults to... /opt/bcc/tests/screenshots/
print.screen.path

# Base server path
# Defaults to value in config.properties which is normally http://localhost:8080
server.path

# The lead in page for the birth regstrations process
# Defaults to... /home/page/-/item/servicepage/44
birth.registrations.home.page

An example mvn call with configurations is as follows:-
mvn integration-tests -Dresource.path=/home/testuser/liferay-tests-portal/BCCPortal2/src/main/resources -Dprint.screen.path=/home/testuser/tests/screenprints -Dserver.path=http://l-dssdev-app1.bcc.lan:8080/ -Dbirth.registrations.home.page=/web/guest/lead-in